column5: Am fishing Dinorwic,W.O. June 09,for the 1st time.Any help on walleye and smallies will be appreciated. :7

I have fished the Dinorwic chain for over 10 yrs. In june some of the best results have been fishing Butler. There is a rocky point just prior to entering Butler and once in Butler, go about a mile, then off to the right past the first island. between the first and next Island. This is a shallow flat with cabbage weed that has done well for me. Let us know what worked for you.
